# Keras Model Summaries

This page lists the model structure of all Keras models currently supported
in WekaDeeplearning4j. You may want to use these as a reference when using different
feature extraction layers, or simply as a learning tool for looking at different architectures.

These were generated by Keras from the `keras_download.py` script in this package.
